.DT
adjust_al
$MUDNAME$ creator help
adjust_al

Name
.SI 5
Adjusts a living objects alignment.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
int adjust_al( int number )
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This is one of two alignment adjustment functions (the other being
adjust_alignment()).  Adjust_al is generally more true, in that it
will add the number straight to the existing alignment.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
query_al, set_al, adjust_alignment, align_string
.EP
